text: Colobothea fasciata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Bates in 1865. It is known from Argentina, Brazil and Paraguay.BioLib.cz - Colobothea fasciata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Colobotheini Category:Beetles described in 1865
title: Colobothea fasciata
